            <title>1.0.6</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 22:27:54 -0300</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>7</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.6</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.6</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Terminals 1.0.6

- **Hooks dos CLIs (Claude/Codex/Gemini)**: corrigido o erro `Stop hook error: /bin/sh: /dev/tty: Device not configured` que aparecia no Claude Code em algumas instalações. Os hooks agora escrevem no path absoluto do PTY (`TERMINALS_PTY_PATH`, exportado pelo shell), em vez de depender do `/dev/tty` que falha quando o dispatcher de hooks spawna subprocessos sem controlling-tty.
]]></description>
            <enclosure url="https://github.com/alisonzigulich/terminals-releases/releases/download/v1.0.6/Terminals-1.0.6.zip" length="16327195" type="application/octet-stream" sparkle:edSignature="DwI7VpkHAIw6xVBaivjNMdXHxr2D3C4mbAJUDj6x+c+pMCba0CTFfVXqLNYYGx5/AF6BkCeVrT5s5POKd6cLCQ=="/>
